//----- Green flag events ---------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------

WhenGreenFlagClicked()
{
    Load Rom Flag = 0;
    If (coolnes_regenerate == 1)
    {
        Looks.SwitchBackdropTo(Gradient2);
        GUItemp = "Rebuilding Tables...";
        Variable.Show(GUItemp);
        Event.BroadcastAndWait("make_tables");
        coolnes_regenerate = 0;
    }
    Variable.Hide(GUItemp);
    MenuScroll = -400;
    Event.Broadcast("exit emulator");
}


//----- Broadcast received events -------------------------------------------------------------------------------------

WhenBroadcastReceived(exit emulator)
{
    Theme Switch Flag = 0;
    Sound.StopAllSounds();
    Looks.SwitchBackdropTo(Menu Theme[2]);
    Pen.Clear();
    microbit_displayClear ?? - probably legacy function from Scratch 2.0;
    Sound.SetVolumeTo(100);
    Forever
    {
        Sound.PlayUntilDone((Menu Theme[1] + 2));
    }
}

WhenBroadcastReceived(exit emulator)
{
    Control.Wait(2);
    Forever
    {
        If (Not ((Inemu? == 1)))
        {
            If ((Sensing.KeyPressed(right arrow) Or Sensing.KeyPressed(d)) Or microbit_isTilted ?? - probably legacy function from Scratch 2.0)
            {
                Sound.Play((1 + Menu Theme[7]));
                Repeat ((4 * (is compiled? + 1)))
                {
                    MenuScroll += (-50 / (is compiled? + 1));
                }
                If ((-1800 > MenuScroll) Or (Not (((MenuScroll % 200) == 0))))
                {
                    MenuScroll = 200;
                }
                Control.Wait(0.1);
            }
            If ((Sensing.KeyPressed(left arrow) Or Sensing.KeyPressed(a)) Or microbit_isTilted ?? - probably legacy function from Scratch 2.0)
            {
                Sound.Play((1 + Menu Theme[7]));
                Repeat ((4 * (is compiled? + 1)))
                {
                    MenuScroll += (50 / (is compiled? + 1));
                }
                If ((MenuScroll > 200) Or (Not (((MenuScroll % 200) == 0))))
                {
                    MenuScroll = -1800;
                }
                Control.Wait(0.1);
            }
            If (((Sensing.KeyPressed(space) Or Sensing.KeyPressed(enter)) Or microbit_isButtonPressed ?? - probably legacy function from Scratch 2.0) And ((MenuScroll % 200) == 0))
            {
                Event.Broadcast("GUI_Emulator_Select");
                If ((-200 > MenuScroll) And (Romimportflag == 0))
                {
                    Stop(other scripts in sprite);
                    Stop(this script);
                }
                Else
                {
                    Wait Until (Not (((Sensing.KeyPressed(space) Or Sensing.KeyPressed(enter)) Or microbit_isButtonPressed ?? - probably legacy function from Scratch 2.0)));
                }
            }
        }
    }
}

WhenBroadcastReceived(get_theme)
{
    microbit_displaySymbol ?? - probably legacy function from Scratch 2.0;
    Sensing.Ask(Operator.Join("Paste your 8-digit theme code now. (Current code: ", Operator.Join(Operator.Join(Operator.Join(Operator.Join(Menu Theme[1], Menu Theme[2]), Operator.Join(Menu Theme[3], Menu Theme[4])), Operator.Join(Operator.Join(Menu Theme[5], Menu Theme[6]), Operator.Join(Menu Theme[7], Menu Theme[8]))), ")")));
    Call decrypt(Sensing.Answer());
    microbit_displayClear ?? - probably legacy function from Scratch 2.0;
    Theme Switch Flag = 1;
    Event.Broadcast("Launch Emulator");
}

WhenBroadcastReceived(Launch Emulator)
{
    Stop(other scripts in sprite);
    Repeat (10)
    {
        Sound.ChangeVolumeBy(-10);
    }
    Sound.StopAllSounds();
    If (Theme Switch Flag == 1)
    {
        Event.BroadcastAndWait("Launch EmulatorWaitd");
        Event.Broadcast("exit emulator");
    }
}


//----- Custom blocks -------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------

Define decrypt(string Decryption) (warp=false)
{
    If (Variable.Length(Decryption) > 0)
    {
        If (Decryption == "random")
        {
            List.ReplaceItem(Menu Theme, 1, Operator.Random(1 / 6));
            List.ReplaceItem(Menu Theme, 2, Operator.Random(1 / 9));
            List.ReplaceItem(Menu Theme, 3, Operator.Random(2 / 4));
            List.ReplaceItem(Menu Theme, 4, Operator.Random(0 / 1));
            List.ReplaceItem(Menu Theme, 5, Operator.Random(0 / 9));
            List.ReplaceItem(Menu Theme, 6, Operator.Random(0 / 9));
            List.ReplaceItem(Menu Theme, 7, Operator.Random(0 / 1));
            List.ReplaceItem(Menu Theme, 8, Operator.Random(0 / 1));
        }
        Else
        {
            List.DeleteAll(Menu Theme);
            Accumulator = 0;
            Repeat (Variable.Length(Decryption))
            {
                Accumulator += 1;
                List.Add(Menu Theme, Operator.LetterOf(Decryption, Accumulator));
            }
        }
    }
    Else
    {
        List.ReplaceItem(Menu Theme, 1, 1);
        List.ReplaceItem(Menu Theme, 2, 1);
        List.ReplaceItem(Menu Theme, 3, 2);
        List.ReplaceItem(Menu Theme, 4, 3);
        List.ReplaceItem(Menu Theme, 5, 0);
        List.ReplaceItem(Menu Theme, 6, 0);
        List.ReplaceItem(Menu Theme, 7, 0);
        List.ReplaceItem(Menu Theme, 8, 0);
    }
}
